<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="ltr" lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Password Reset — PetroFlow ERP</title>
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f6f9; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a56db 0%, #0e3fa1 100%); padding: 32px; text-align: center; }
  .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .logo { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .body { padding: 36px 40px; }
  .body p { color: #374151; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 15px; }
  .btn { display: inline-block; margin: 24px 0; padding: 14px 32px; background: #1a56db; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; }
  .note { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 16px; }
  .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 24px 0; }
  .footer { background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">🛢️</div>
    <h1>PetroFlow ERP</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <p>Hello <strong>{{ fullName }}</strong>,</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset the password for your PetroFlow ERP account. Click the button below to create a new password:</p>
    <div style="text-align:center;">
      <a href="{{ resetLink }}" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
    </div>
    <p class="note">⏱ This link will expire in <strong>{{ expiresInMinutes }} minutes</strong>.</p>
    <hr class="divider">
    <p class="note">If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
    <p class="note">For security, do not share this link with anyone.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    &copy; 2026 PetroFlow ERP. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
